data.chText: 令人大为惊奇的；（尤指）令人惊喜（或惊羡、惊叹）的
data.enText: very surprising, especially in a way that makes you feel pleasure or admiration

data.chText: 惊人的成就 / 发现 / 成功 / 表演
人适应环境的速度之快真是惊人。
data.enText: It's amazing how quickly people adapt.

data.chText: 令人惊奇的是，竟没有人注意到。

means: (尤指)令人惊喜(或惊羡、惊叹)的

tr: inspiring awe or admiration or wonder
example: New York is an amazing city
the Grand Canyon is an awe-inspiring sight
the awesome complexity of the universe
this sea, whose gently awful stirrings seem to speak of some hidden soul beneath"- Melvill
Westminster Hall's awing majesty, so vast, so high, so silent
she does an amazing amount of work
the dog was capable of astonishing tricks

value.def: You say that something is amazing when it is very surprising and makes you feel pleasure, approval, or wonder.

example.ex: It's amazing what we can remember with a little prompting...
example.tran: 稍加提醒我们就能想起很多东西，真是让人惊奇。

example.ex: This movie has some of the most amazing stunts you're ever likely to see.
example.tran: 这部电影里有一些可能是你见所未见、让人惊叹的特技。

example.ex: She was an amazingly good cook.
example.tran: 她是个厨艺精湛的厨师。

trans: 奇迹诞生之地；奇迹在这里发生
冰雕爆破者；惊艳爆破；冰雕爆破；爆冰

types.define: 《amazing》是上影集团与美国篮球协会(NBA)首度合作的一部以篮球为主题的励志影片，讲述了一个关于篮球、青春、奋斗、爱情的精彩故事。该片演员阵容豪华，包括了国内一线明星黄晓明、香港著名演员、导演冯德伦、韩国人气演员与模特金雅中、台湾著名主持人黑人(陈建州)以及在新版《红楼梦》中饰演少年宝钗的李沁。
